Sensor Based Aquaponics Fish Pond Dataset

Source: https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/ogbuokiriblessing/sensor-based-aquaponics-fish-pond-datasets

Columns:
created_at - Timestamp (CET timezone)
entry_id - Entry identifier
Temperature (C) - Water temperature in Celsius
Turbidity(NTU) - Turbidity in Nephelometric Turbidity Units
Dissolved Oxygen(g/ml)- Dissolved oxygen concentration
PH - Water pH level
Ammonia(g/ml) - Ammonia concentration
Nitrate(g/ml) - Nitrate concentration
Population - Fish population count
Fish_Length(cm) - Average fish length in centimeters
Fish_Weight(g) - Average fish weight in grams
